psychology of the human mind.

00:00:32.450 --> 00:00:34.370 align:middle line:84%
And with us today
is Jonathan Zap.

00:00:34.370 --> 00:00:37.490 align:middle line:84%
Jonathan is a
author, researcher,

00:00:37.490 --> 00:00:41.735 align:middle line:84%
paranormal investigator, and an
expert on Jungian philosophy.

00:00:41.735 --> 00:00:43.490 align:middle line:84%
Jonathan, welcome
to "Beyond Belief."

00:00:43.490 --> 00:00:44.990 align:middle line:84%
>>JONATHAN ZAP:
Thank you very much.

00:00:44.990 --> 00:00:46.670 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You remind
me of an actor

00:00:46.670 --> 00:00:49.700 align:middle line:90%
who played in "Roger Rabbit."

00:00:49.700 --> 00:00:51.320 align:middle line:90%
